    "headline": "A collective of",
    "headlineAccent": "changemakers",
    "description1": "Sarthi is a youth-driven nonprofit founded on the belief that young people are not the leaders of tomorrow — they are the leaders of today. We empower students and young professionals to take ownership of local challenges and build solutions that last.",
